6. **Highlighting** — `highlightMatch` splits on the query (capturing group) and wraps matches in `<mark>`.
7. **"No results found"** — rendered when the filtered list is empty and we're not mid-search.
8. **Cleanup on unmount** — the `useEffect` returns `clearTimeout`, which runs on unmount and before each re-run.
